des:
Stock Info skill provides you the quote of any stock listed on US stock exchange.

-It is not intended for commercial use and provider/author is not responsible for your stock investment decisions.
- Quotes may be delayed due to market restrictions.
-Uses Alpha Vantage API to get current stock information.
-You can also ask with with stock name
